41:34.090 --> 41:37.093
But look at this as a chance to do even better.

41:37.719 --> 41:41.222
Use that good will to create an experience

41:41.222 --> 41:43.515
no one is expecting.

41:43.515 --> 41:45.475
Yeah.

41:45.475 --> 41:46.977
Yeah.

41:46.977 --> 41:48.645
Waiter good Sir.

41:48.645 --> 41:50.897
This is not a blank page,

41:50.897 --> 41:53.900
