43:13.807 --> 43:15.558
How's registration?

43:15.558 --> 43:18.353
Ugh, don’t remind me.

43:18.978 --> 43:23.900
Back in my day it was waiting in long lines
to hand in your papers,

43:23.900 --> 43:26.319
