43:52.426 --> 43:55.762
And I guess you can tell...

43:55.762 --> 43:58.431
this isn't my usual place.

43:59.598 --> 44:01.184
Well,

44:01.184 --> 44:04.437
I think you stick out wherever you go.

44:04.437 --> 44:06.730
In a good way.

44:08.649 --> 44:11.652
