47:22.661 --> 47:25.663
So don’t fear this blossoming union,

47:25.663 --> 47:27.249
Embrace it.

47:27.249 --> 47:28.875
That...

47:29.585 --> 47:32.045
That, that was beautiful.

47:32.045 --> 47:33.254
Yeah.

47:34.005 --> 47:37.842
Yeah.
[WAITER] Now, Get back out there..

47:37.842 --> 47:40.094
