47:55.317 --> 47:58.194
So punctual arrival, check.

47:58.194 --> 48:00.529
Witty banter, check and check.

48:00.529 --> 48:03.782
Don’t forget undercover handsome.
I heard that’s the best kind.

48:03.782 --> 48:07.869
Don’t make me get the bad list out.
[SALEEM] Okay.

48:09.245 --> 48:14.542
So according to the dating rules handed
down from high above...

48:14.542 --> 48:17.753
This new phase requires a change in conversation.

48:17.753 --> 48:21.006
from pleasantries to something deeper.

48:21.006 --> 48:23.884
Like life goals, favorite movies.

48:23.884 --> 48:26.095
Exactly, all that good stuff.

48:26.095 --> 48:28.514
Okay. Fine.

48:30.307 --> 48:31.724
Family?

48:31.724 --> 48:34.395
Oh geez Saleem, going with the heavy hitters already.

48:34.395 --> 48:36.771
But you said deeper!

48:36.771 --> 48:40.233
I’m just joking. What do you want to know.

48:40.942 --> 48:42.151
Parents?

48:42.151 --> 48:44.654
Yes; two of them like everyone else.

48:44.654 --> 48:46.738
Happily married 28 long years.

48:46.738 --> 48:49.741
And of course you're an only child.

48:49.741 --> 48:52.035
Yes how did you...

48:54.704 --> 48:56.415
...shut the fuck up.

48:56.415 --> 48:57.457
Fine.

48:57.457 --> 49:00.251
what’s the most embarrassing thing to happen to you?

49:00.251 --> 49:02.920
I mean curl up and die type stuff.

49:02.920 --> 49:04.797
I don’t know.

49:04.797 --> 49:06.966
Come on.

49:07.550 --> 49:09.260
Wait, yea. This is really funny.

49:09.718 --> 49:11.970
This is really funny.

49:12.680 --> 49:13.763
Form six graduation.

49:13.763 --> 49:15.683
Oh, this is going to be good.

49:15.683 --> 49:17.767
I wasn’t going to go or anything,

49:17.767 --> 49:22.771
but I got a random call from Alicia Vashti Cooblal.

49:22.771 --> 49:25.190
didn't even think she knew my name

49:26.024 --> 49:30.612
