49:31.071 --> 49:32.406
I said yes.

49:32.573 --> 49:35.159
hung the phone up and immediately started panicking.

49:35.159 --> 49:38.620
Not the good kind of panicing, not the
excited kind but more like...

49:38.620 --> 49:40.539
Fear.

49:40.872 --> 49:43.374
Two weeks later I show up at her house

49:43.374 --> 49:48.837
with my blue corsage, matching the blue shirt
Abeerah told me to buy.

49:49.213 --> 49:52.215
Her dad answered the door and

49:52.340 --> 49:56.803
He says she already left with her boyfriend.

49:57.262 --> 49:58.722
Oh Saleem.

49:58.722 --> 50:00.848
No it’s okay.

50:00.848 --> 50:02.225
It's fine.

50:02.225 --> 50:04.436
Turns out she...

50:05.102 --> 50:08.105
was just asking me to get her boyfriend angry

50:08.105 --> 50:11.108
and never bothered to let me in on the plan.

50:24.037 --> 50:25.163
You know what!

50:25.163 --> 50:28.165
I’m going to call that bitch right now.

50:30.876 --> 50:32.587
What are you doing?

50:32.587 --> 50:35.589
You’re being very rude. I’m on the phone.

50:35.964 --> 50:37.633
Sorry.

50:38.759 --> 50:43.680
Oh, good evening. Is a miss Alicia Vashti Cooblal available.

50:43.680 --> 50:48.768
Oh, I’m sorry Mrs. Alicia Vashti Mohammed.

50:49.060 --> 50:51.145
