[SALEEM] Okay.

50:59.361 --> 51:03.406
Oh hello Alicia. Alicia from...

51:04.616 --> 51:05.659
ASJA

51:05.659 --> 51:08.703
licia from ASJA Girls class of 2010.

51:08.703 --> 51:10.955
