52:38.745 --> 52:43.081
Your meals maybe a bit longer in preparation than usual.

52:43.081 --> 52:44.791
It’s okay.

52:46.084 --> 52:47.711
You okay?

52:48.085 --> 52:52.883
Ahhh Wine. Must be some really big disturbance.

52:52.883 --> 52:56.677
Oh no no no mam.

52:57.345 --> 53:00.348
Nothing out of the ordinary.
[GRACE] I’m surprised.

53:00.348 --> 53:05.060
