of any kind.

53:05.060 --> 53:06.561
What do you think Saleem?

53:06.561 --> 53:08.688
Salmonella?

53:12.066 --> 53:13.902
Oh no!

53:13.902 --> 53:16.821
An establishment of this quality.

53:16.821 --> 53:19.824
I would guess something along the lines of...

53:19.824 --> 53:22.451
an illegal workforce,

53:23.452 --> 53:25.954
There is no...

53:25.954 --> 53:28.540
Interesting. Why not both?

53:28.540 --> 53:31.542
Takes a village right?
[GRACE] Yes.

53:38.716 --> 53:39.717
Your meals.

53:39.717 --> 53:44.262
I will check on the progress of your meals at once!

53:49.101 --> 53:50.894
You're evil.

53:51.937 --> 53:53.187
Was that mean?

53:53.187 --> 53:55.607
Depends how you look at it.

53:55.607 --> 53:57.483
