54:29.346 --> 54:35.351
...and that’s how I learnt to never check the mail just
wearing a thong.

54:36.979 --> 54:38.604
What?

54:38.604 --> 54:40.815
just seeing if you were with me.

54:41.357 --> 54:44.360
Sorry. I’m just mentally tapped out.

54:45.193 --> 54:47.404
Okay.
[GRACE] No no no.

54:48.030 --> 54:50.950
Its just the natural trajectory of the night.

54:50.950 --> 54:53.160
