55:18.308 --> 55:21.311
I could ask for a beer bottle if it would make
you feel better.

55:21.311 --> 55:25.940
Oh shut up and continue with your clever little metaphor

55:27.232 --> 55:29.401
So THIS is me.
[GRACE] Yes.

55:29.401 --> 55:31.570
And This is you.

55:34.490 --> 55:36.282
Hey!

55:36.282 --> 55:38.201
Just trying to be accurate.

55:38.201 --> 55:42.080
Well that salt shakers a bit big if you ask me.

55:42.371 --> 55:45.374
Come on. I’m liking where this is going.

55:52.089 --> 55:53.590
I’m at a loss.

55:53.590 --> 55:55.425
You?

55:55.425 --> 55:58.678
Yea. I did not think this would require so much plot.

55:58.678 --> 56:01.138
Come, give me those.

56:03.600 --> 56:06.853
You are the salt.

56:08.145 --> 56:11.398
People don’t realize how much they need you,

56:11.398 --> 56:16.236
but you are always around and reliable

56:17.655 --> 56:20.657
so its easy to take you for granted.

56:22.700 --> 56:27.539
But if you are missing from a meal,
you bet people will notice.

56:29.833 --> 56:31.583
And I’m the pepper.

56:31.583 --> 56:34.503
People tend to not like me at first, but

56:34.503 --> 56:37.798
