56:41.677 --> 56:42.886
Grace!

56:43.971 --> 56:47.723
But when you mix them just right,

56:49.308 --> 56:51.310
they’re perfect.

56:55.022 --> 56:58.025
And who doesn’t like salt and pepper?

57:12.746 --> 57:15.749
I feel like we they definitely came after us.

57:16.333 --> 57:19.128
I know they came after us.

57:19.128 --> 57:22.131
Come on this is ridiculous.

57:23.631 --> 57:26.051
You want to dine and ditch?

57:27.468 --> 57:29.888
Well this will be just ditching right?
[SALEEM] No

57:29.888 --> 57:31.014
We got the wine.

57:31.014 --> 57:32.389
