57:32.389 --> 57:34.017
Yea but we got it.

57:34.934 --> 57:36.144
Yeah.

57:38.021 --> 57:39.938
Oh but that poor waiter though.

57:39.938 --> 57:43.066
Yeah, I know maybe we should

57:43.942 --> 57:46.611
Oh shit I hear him coming.

