[GRACE] Umm

1:00:23.006 --> 1:00:25.049
Na. Just go ahead.

1:00:25.049 --> 1:00:26.008
You sure?

1:00:26.008 --> 1:00:29.970
Yes! Pull the band aid man.

1:00:29.970 --> 1:00:31.930
Okay.

1:00:34.724 --> 1:00:38.353
Hey. We got this.

1:00:39.645 --> 1:00:41.939
Hope so.

1:01:28.524 --> 1:01:33.112
Hi, merry chris, happy holidays sir. I’m Saleem.

1:01:33.112 --> 1:01:36.240
Well hello there partner.

1:01:36.240 --> 1:01:39.993
Of course, Gracey told us a lot about you.

1:01:39.993 --> 1:01:43.830
And while I appreciate the sir sentiment

1:01:43.830 --> 1:01:45.915
you can stick with Pete.

1:01:45.915 --> 1:01:47.375
